headline: Medtronic (MDT) Valuation: Assessing Potential After Raised Outlook and Strong Quarterly Growth
summary: Medtronic (MDT) gave investors something to talk about after reporting higher sales and profits compared to last year, and raising its outlook for both revenue and earnings.
